  <entry>
    <title>Install Softwares for High-energy Astronomy</title>
    <link href="https://blog.fxzheng.com/2015/10/18/high-energy-soft-install/"/>
    <id>https://blog.fxzheng.com/2015/10/18/high-energy-soft-install/</id>
    <published>2015-10-18T00:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2016-05-02T07:58:35.309Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html">


&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-1&quot; class=&quot;outline-2&quot;&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;sec-1&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-2&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; Introduction&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-2&quot; id=&quot;text-1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
This is a brief instruction of installing softwares for high-energy
astronomy under &lt;code&gt;Archlinux&lt;/code&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-2&quot; class=&quot;outline-2&quot;&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;sec-2&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-2&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt; DS9&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-2&quot; id=&quot;text-2&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-2-1&quot; class=&quot;outline-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;sec-2-1&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-3&quot;&gt;2.1&lt;/span&gt; Install&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-3&quot; id=&quot;text-2-1&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;org-src-container&quot;&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight sh&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;yaourt -S ds9-bin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;a id=&quot;more&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-3&quot; class=&quot;outline-2&quot;&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;sec-3&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-2&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt; HEASOFT&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-2&quot; id=&quot;text-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-3-1&quot; class=&quot;outline-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;sec-3-1&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-3&quot;&gt;3.1&lt;/span&gt; Download&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-3&quot; id=&quot;text-3-1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
Visit &lt;a href=&quot;http://heasarc.gsfc.nasa.gov/docs/software/lheasoft/download.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;external&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; to download the source code
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-3-2&quot; class=&quot;outline-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;sec-3-2&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-3&quot;&gt;3.2&lt;/span&gt; Unpack to the installation directory&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-3&quot; id=&quot;text-3-2&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;org-src-container&quot;&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight sh&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;built_in&quot;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; /usr/&lt;span class=&quot;built_in&quot;&gt;local&lt;/span&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;sudo tar zxvf /path/to/the/downloaded/file/heasoft-&lt;span class=&quot;number&quot;&gt;6.17&lt;/span&gt;src.tar.gz&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-3-3&quot; class=&quot;outline-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;sec-3-3&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-3&quot;&gt;3.3&lt;/span&gt; Install&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-3&quot; id=&quot;text-3-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;org-src-container&quot;&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight sh&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;built_in&quot;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; heasoft-&lt;span class=&quot;number&quot;&gt;6.17&lt;/span&gt;/BUILD_DIR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;sudo ./configure&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;sudo make&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;sudo make install&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
this may take some time, so be patient : -) or you can have a coffee ~
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-3-4&quot; class=&quot;outline-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;sec-3-4&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-3&quot;&gt;3.4&lt;/span&gt; Set environment&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-3&quot; id=&quot;text-3-4&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
Add following code to your &lt;code&gt;~/.bashrc&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;~/.zshrc&lt;/code&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;org-src-container&quot;&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight sh&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;built_in&quot;&gt;export&lt;/span&gt; HEADAS=/usr/&lt;span class=&quot;built_in&quot;&gt;local&lt;/span&gt;/heasoft-&lt;span class=&quot;number&quot;&gt;6.17&lt;/span&gt;/(PLATFORM)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;built_in&quot;&gt;alias&lt;/span&gt; heainit=&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;. &lt;span class=&quot;variable&quot;&gt;$HEADAS&lt;/span&gt;/headas-init.sh&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
where (PLATFORM) is a placeholder for the platform-specific string 
denoting your machine&amp;apos;s architecture, for example: &lt;code&gt;x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu-libc2. 22&lt;/code&gt;
in my Archlinux
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-3-5&quot; class=&quot;outline-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;sec-3-5&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-3&quot;&gt;3.5&lt;/span&gt; Check&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-3&quot; id=&quot;text-3-5&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
Run &lt;code&gt;heainit&lt;/code&gt; in your unix prompt
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-4&quot; class=&quot;outline-2&quot;&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;sec-4&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-2&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt; XMM SAS&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-2&quot; id=&quot;text-4&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-4-1&quot; class=&quot;outline-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;sec-4-1&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-3&quot;&gt;4.1&lt;/span&gt; Download&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-3&quot; id=&quot;text-4-1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
Download from &lt;a href=&quot;http://xmm.esac.esa.int/sas/current/downloadandinstall.shtml&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;external&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-4-2&quot; class=&quot;outline-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;sec-4-2&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-3&quot;&gt;4.2&lt;/span&gt; Unpack&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-3&quot; id=&quot;text-4-2&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;org-src-container&quot;&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight sh&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;sudo mkdir /usr/&lt;span class=&quot;built_in&quot;&gt;local&lt;/span&gt;/SAS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;built_in&quot;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; /usr/&lt;span class=&quot;built_in&quot;&gt;local&lt;/span&gt;/SAS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;sudo tar zxf /path/to/the/downloaded/file/sas_14.&lt;span class=&quot;number&quot;&gt;0.0&lt;/span&gt;-&amp;lt;OS&amp;gt;.tgz&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-4-3&quot; class=&quot;outline-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;sec-4-3&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-3&quot;&gt;4.3&lt;/span&gt; Run the installation file&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-3&quot; id=&quot;text-4-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;org-src-container&quot;&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight sh&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;sudo ./install.sh&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-4-4&quot; class=&quot;outline-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;sec-4-4&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-3&quot;&gt;4.4&lt;/span&gt; Set environment&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-3&quot; id=&quot;text-4-4&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
Add following code to your &lt;code&gt;~/.bashrc&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;~/.zshrc&lt;/code&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;org-src-container&quot;&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight sh&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;built_in&quot;&gt;alias&lt;/span&gt; sasinit=&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;. /usr/local/SAS/xmmsas_20141104_1833/setsas.sh&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-4-5&quot; class=&quot;outline-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;sec-4-5&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-3&quot;&gt;4.5&lt;/span&gt; Check&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-3&quot; id=&quot;text-4-5&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
Run &lt;code&gt;sasinit&lt;/code&gt; in your unix prompt
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-5&quot; class=&quot;outline-2&quot;&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;sec-5&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-2&quot;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt; CALDB&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-2&quot; id=&quot;text-5&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-5-1&quot; class=&quot;outline-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;sec-5-1&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-3&quot;&gt;5.1&lt;/span&gt; Download&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-3&quot; id=&quot;text-5-1&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;org-ul&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Chandra

&lt;p&gt;
Visit &lt;a href=&quot;http://cxc.harvard.edu/ciao/download/caldb.html#caldb&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;external&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; to download Chandra caldb
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Others

&lt;p&gt;
Visit &lt;a href=&quot;http://heasarc.gsfc.nasa.gov/docs/heasarc/caldb/caldb_supported_missions.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;external&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; to download caldb of missions needed such as &lt;code&gt;Suzaku&lt;/code&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-5-2&quot; class=&quot;outline-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;sec-5-2&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-3&quot;&gt;5.2&lt;/span&gt; Unpack&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-3&quot; id=&quot;text-5-2&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;org-src-container&quot;&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight sh&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;mkdir ~/caldb&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;built_in&quot;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; ~/caldb&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;tar zxvf /path/to/the/downloaded/file/caldb_4.&lt;span class=&quot;number&quot;&gt;6.9&lt;/span&gt;_main.tar.gz&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;tar zxvf /path/to/the/downloaded/file/goodfiles_suzaku_xis_bcf_20151005.tar.gz&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;tar zxvf /path/to/the/downloaded/file/goodfiles_suzaku_xis_cpf_20151005.tar.gz&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;tar zxvf /path/to/the/downloaded/file/goodfiles_suzaku_xis_index_20151005.tar.gz&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-5-3&quot; class=&quot;outline-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;sec-5-3&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-3&quot;&gt;5.3&lt;/span&gt; Set environment&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-3&quot; id=&quot;text-5-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
Add following code to your &lt;code&gt;~/.bashrc&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;~/.zshrc&lt;/code&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;org-src-container&quot;&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight sh&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;built_in&quot;&gt;export&lt;/span&gt; CALDB=&lt;span class=&quot;variable&quot;&gt;$HOME&lt;/span&gt;/caldb&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;built_in&quot;&gt;export&lt;/span&gt; CALDBCONFIG=&lt;span class=&quot;variable&quot;&gt;$CALDB&lt;/span&gt;/software/tools/caldb.config&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;built_in&quot;&gt;export&lt;/span&gt; CALDBALIAS=&lt;span class=&quot;variable&quot;&gt;$CALDB&lt;/span&gt;/software/tools/&lt;span class=&quot;built_in&quot;&gt;alias&lt;/span&gt;_config.fits&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-6&quot; class=&quot;outline-2&quot;&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;sec-6&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-2&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt; CIAO&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-2&quot; id=&quot;text-6&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-6-1&quot; class=&quot;outline-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;sec-6-1&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-3&quot;&gt;6.1&lt;/span&gt; Before installation&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-3&quot; id=&quot;text-6-1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
link installed CALDB to your CIAO installation directory
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;org-src-container&quot;&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight sh&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;ln &lt;span class=&quot;operator&quot;&gt;-s&lt;/span&gt; ~/caldb ~/ciao-&lt;span class=&quot;number&quot;&gt;4.7&lt;/span&gt;/CALDB&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-6-2&quot; class=&quot;outline-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;sec-6-2&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-3&quot;&gt;6.2&lt;/span&gt; Download &lt;code&gt;ciao-install&lt;/code&gt; and run it&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-3&quot; id=&quot;text-6-2&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
Download from &lt;a href=&quot;http://cxc.harvard.edu/ciao/download/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;external&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;org-src-container&quot;&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight sh&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;./ciao-install&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
just install ciao to your home directory : -)
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-6-3&quot; class=&quot;outline-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;sec-6-3&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-3&quot;&gt;6.3&lt;/span&gt; Install dependences&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-3&quot; id=&quot;text-6-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;org-src-container&quot;&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight sh&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;yaourt -S libselinux&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
and any other if required
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-6-4&quot; class=&quot;outline-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;sec-6-4&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-3&quot;&gt;6.4&lt;/span&gt; Fix a bug&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-3&quot; id=&quot;text-6-4&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
I got something like:
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre class=&quot;example&quot;&gt;
sh: symbol lookup error: sh: undefined symbol: rl_signal_event_hook
&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
duckduckgoaround, I figured out the following solution:
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;org-src-container&quot;&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight sh&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;built_in&quot;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; ~/ciao-&lt;span class=&quot;number&quot;&gt;4.7&lt;/span&gt;/ots/lib/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;mv libreadline.so.&lt;span class=&quot;number&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt; libreadline.so.&lt;span class=&quot;number&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;.bak&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;mv libreadline.so libreadline.so.bak&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;ln &lt;span class=&quot;operator&quot;&gt;-s&lt;/span&gt; /usr/lib/libreadline.so.&lt;span class=&quot;number&quot;&gt;6.3&lt;/span&gt; ~/ciao-&lt;span class=&quot;number&quot;&gt;4.7&lt;/span&gt;/ots/lib/libreadline.so.&lt;span class=&quot;number&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;ln &lt;span class=&quot;operator&quot;&gt;-s&lt;/span&gt; /usr/lib/libreadline.so.&lt;span class=&quot;number&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt; ~/ciao-&lt;span class=&quot;number&quot;&gt;4.7&lt;/span&gt;/ots/lib/libreadline.so&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-6-5&quot; class=&quot;outline-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;sec-6-5&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-3&quot;&gt;6.5&lt;/span&gt; Set environment&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-3&quot; id=&quot;text-6-5&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
Add following code to your &lt;code&gt;~/.bashrc&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;~/.zshrc&lt;/code&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;org-src-container&quot;&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight sh&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;built_in&quot;&gt;alias&lt;/span&gt; ciao=&lt;span class=&quot;string&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;source ~/ciao-4.7/bin/ciao.bash&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-6-6&quot; class=&quot;outline-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;sec-6-6&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-3&quot;&gt;6.6&lt;/span&gt; Check&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-3&quot; id=&quot;text-6-6&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;org-src-container&quot;&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight sh&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;ciao&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;check_ciao_caldb&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-7&quot; class=&quot;outline-2&quot;&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;sec-7&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-2&quot;&gt;7&lt;/span&gt; ISIS&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-2&quot; id=&quot;text-7&quot;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-7-1&quot; class=&quot;outline-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;sec-7-1&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-3&quot;&gt;7.1&lt;/span&gt; Install dependencies&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-3&quot; id=&quot;text-7-1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
Make sure that &lt;code&gt;slang&lt;/code&gt; has been installed
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-7-2&quot; class=&quot;outline-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;sec-7-2&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-3&quot;&gt;7.2&lt;/span&gt; Clone source by git&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-3&quot; id=&quot;text-7-2&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;org-src-container&quot;&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight sh&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;git &lt;span class=&quot;built_in&quot;&gt;clone&lt;/span&gt; http://space.mit.edu/cxc/isis/isis.git ~/Downloads/isis-src&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-7-3&quot; class=&quot;outline-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;sec-7-3&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-3&quot;&gt;7.3&lt;/span&gt; Build and install&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-3&quot; id=&quot;text-7-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;org-src-container&quot;&gt;

&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight sh&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;built_in&quot;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; ~/Downloads/isis-src&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;./configure --with-headas=&lt;span class=&quot;variable&quot;&gt;$HEADAS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;make&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;make check&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;sudo make install&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id=&quot;outline-container-sec-7-4&quot; class=&quot;outline-3&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;sec-7-4&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;section-number-3&quot;&gt;7.4&lt;/span&gt; Check installation&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;outline-text-3&quot; id=&quot;text-7-4&quot;&gt;
